{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e4e413a611","title":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建革造会联络站负责人讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"29bbdf4214","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"e4e413a611","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ba0bf5e58e","type":"title","text":"周恩来陈伯达接见福建革造会联络站负责人讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70d2d91db5","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf39e0b75a","type":"paragraph","text":"同志啊！同志啊！你们眼光太短了，什么矛盾很大，哪里有与蒋介石矛盾大？蒋介石打过来你们连自己家乡也保不住，还能够安心这样搞文化大革命？！现在矛盾的主要方面在革造会！不在军区，知道吗？","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e4005f51e","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉出了个陈再道，全国就到处揪陈再道，这是对我们伟大军队的污蔑！革造会要听中央的话，要拥护那个八条。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dff83c277","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要顾全大局不要动摇军队不要自毁长城，现在已经到了不能容忍的时候了，今天毛主席批发了九五命令，说今后再夺枪就是反革命行动了。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffdb69f200","type":"paragraph","text":"总理指示说：你们有两个任务：一要有敌情观念，共同对敌；第二要团结大多数，搞好革命三结合，进行大批判。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cce6aa00e","type":"paragraph","text":"会后总理、伯达接见绍安代表。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63bd591d92","type":"paragraph","text":"临走时，对绍安代表说，你们回去后不要搞分裂，要坚持大联合大批判！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4e413a611","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}